Usage: cardano-cli conway stake-address vote-delegation-certificate (--stake-verification-key STRING |

                                                                      --stake-verification-key-file FILEPATH |

                                                                      --stake-key-hash HASH |

                                                                      --stake-script-file FILEPATH |

                                                                      --stake-address ADDRESS)
                                                                    (--drep-script-hash HASH |

                                                                      --drep-verification-key STRING |

                                                                      --drep-verification-key-file FILEPATH |

                                                                      --drep-key-hash HASH |

                                                                      --always-abstain |

                                                                      --always-no-confidence)
                                                                    --out-file FILEPATH

  Create a stake address vote delegation certificate, which when submitted in a
  transaction delegates stake to a DRep.

Available options:
  --stake-verification-key STRING
                           Stake verification key (Bech32 or hex-encoded).
  --stake-verification-key-file FILEPATH
                           Filepath of the staking verification key.
  --stake-key-hash HASH    Stake verification key hash (hex-encoded).
  --stake-script-file FILEPATH
                           Filepath of the staking script.
  --stake-address ADDRESS  Target stake address (bech32 format).
  --drep-script-hash HASH  DRep script hash (hex-encoded). Obtain it with
                           "cardano-cli hash script ...".
  --drep-verification-key STRING
                           DRep verification key (Bech32 or hex-encoded).
  --drep-verification-key-file FILEPATH
                           Filepath of the DRep verification key.
  --drep-key-hash HASH     DRep verification key hash (either Bech32-encoded or
                           hex-encoded).
  --always-abstain         Abstain from voting on all proposals.
  --always-no-confidence   Always vote no confidence
  --out-file FILEPATH      The output file.
  -h,--help                Show this help text
